│ Field                    │ Value                                                                                     │
├──────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ patch_type               │ full                                                                                      │
│ patch_name               │ handcrafted_gait_features_sklearn_ensemble                                                │
│ patch_description        │ Complete architectural redesign abandoning MotionCLIP in favor of handcrafted gait        │
│                          │ features + sklearn classifiers.                                                           │
│                          │                                                                                           │
│                          │ Key changes:                                                                              │
│                          │ 1. **No MotionCLIP dependency** - eliminates the slow, poorly-performing frozen encoder   │
│                          │ that produces generic embeddings unsuitable for PD severity discrimination.               │
│                          │ 2. **Rich handcrafted gait features** - physics-informed features including joint         │
│                          │ statistics, velocities, accelerations, left-right asymmetry, stride frequency via FFT,    │
│                          │ gait regularity via autocorrelation, freeze-of-gait proxies, range of motion, jerk, and   │
│                          │ per-joint energy.                                                                         │
│                          │ 3. **Sklearn classifiers with class_weight='balanced'** - SVM, GradientBoosting, and      │
│                          │ RandomForest in a voting ensemble. These handle the small dataset (781 samples) much      │
│                          │ better than neural networks.                                                              │
│                          │ 4. **StandardScaler normalization** for proper feature scaling.                           │
│                          │ 5. **No GPU needed** - runs entirely on CPU with sklearn, much faster and more reliable.  │
│                          │ 6. **Explicit class 2 recovery** via balanced class weights in all classifiers plus       │
│                          │ SMOTE-like oversampling.                                                                  │
│ num_applied              │ 1                                                                                         │
│ api_costs                │ $0.3638                                                                                   │
